    "description": "Samsung India Electronics has an exciting opening for a Process Engineer at our Howrah office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout Samsung India Electronics:\nSamsung India Electronics is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Monitor equipment performance and coordinate preventive maintenance\n• Manage supplier quality audits and vendor development\n• Implement lean manufacturing and continuous improvement initiatives\n• Implement 5S, Kaizen, and Six Sigma practices on the shop floor\n• Ensure compliance with safety regulations and factory acts\n• Ensure environmental compliance and waste management\n• Coordinate with logistics for dispatching finished goods\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in PLC/SCADA\n• Proficiency in 5S\n• Proficiency in SAP MM/PP\n• Proficiency in ISO 9001\n• Proficiency in Root Cause Analysis\n• Proficiency in APQP\n• Proficiency in AutoCAD\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Learning & development budget\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Howrah, West Bengal, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Samsung India Electronics!",
